    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Soccer Pro Simulator》是一款真实的足球（足球）模拟游戏，让你像明星一样在进球后让观众欢呼。从强力的中场射门到壮观的自行车脚，成为真正的传奇！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/16aa77d4801cca2fc76bd6bc4dc0bedb.webp?t=1772360979\" width=200 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.poster.avif?t=1772360979\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.webm?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.mp4?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《Soccer Pro Simulator》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Soccer Pro Simulator》是一款真实的足球模拟游戏，让玩家沉浸在运动的激情中。像明星一样庆祝不可思议的进球，从强力的中场射门到壮观的自行车脚，所有这一切都由强大的物理引擎驱动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c59edf086a2b3d1e18432c3aeb76e46f.webp?t=1772360979\" width=275 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.poster.avif?t=1772360979\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.webm?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.mp4?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供单人模式与 CPU 对战，在不同的难度下进行对抗，还包含了一个观众模式，让玩家可以观看 CPU 对 CPU 的比赛，提供了引人入胜的游戏体验和真实的比赛场景。提升你的技能和策略，成为球场上的真正传奇！</p>",
